But its only talking, i have no anger against Americans, i could also tell you why from personal experience, i know you are generous people, on more aspects that the average French people i met.<br>
<br>
<br>
Bye,<br>
<br>
<br>
-Belarkan.<br>
<br>
<br>
Oh, before i forget: This is the third time someone tells me that i am very naive if i dont think Irak is related to terrorism.<br>
<br>
But not a single word on why.<br>
Im not going to expand about USA foreign policy since 1945, but for sure, you didnt sit and wait!<br>
If you mean that you do this war because you have the power, huh i guess its true, but then lets not pretend.<br>
This would not be a crusade, nor a fight against evil.<br>
<br>
<br>
So, will you explain me why im truly naive?<br>
